D.E.N.N.I.S
Drinking Everything Never Not Is Sad.

min: 4 Player
max: 10 Player

Pre-Game:
Each Player finds a piece to use during the game.
Players are split into two evenish teams by rolling the DENNIS DICE until 1/2 player are on a team. The teams are Rockhard Red and Bootilitious Blue.
The players must create a DENNIS Board by creating 3 area in which to place their pieces. The areas should be labeled mind, body, ans soul.

When a players piece is in X phase they must drink:
    mind => wine
    body => beer
    soul => liquor
Players start with their piece on the mind spot. You're team can move to the next area by winning a sub-phase.

All Rules of JORKLE SPUNK still apply druring the superphase.

TimeClock:

    Each Phase is 20 minutes.
    An Intermission happens between each sub-phase, the first is 15 minutes the secons is 10 minutes.
    The clock is stopped when the game is not activly being played.
    Each team gets 3, 3 minute timeouts. Any player may use a timeout at anytime.
    A Clockmeister is randomly selected to manage the clock.
    The phase automatically ends when the time is up, unless otherwise specified.

Team JORKLE: 
    *By winning all 3 sub-phases a team is awarded a Team JORKLE

    Team members may unanimously JORKLE a member of the opposing team, 
    or 
    A JORKLE sheild is placed around the team. This protects 1 member from a JORKLE. The sheild breaks after preventing 1 JORKLE.
        *Team members must agree on their decision or loose the reward!

Big D's Shop of Horrors:
    *Zoinks are awarded throughout the superphase

    10 Zoinks => 1 ZORK
    9 Zoinks => 1 JORKLE
    4 Zoinks => 1 point
    1 Zoink => 0.25 points
    4 Zoinks => 1 unit of Alcohol gifted
    25 Zoinks => 10 points

The sub-phases are played in the following order:
    Jiggle Da JORKLE => The Slipery Saucy Gauntley of Sexy Champions x => Fear!

The winner is the team on the farthest space of the board.

